{"tid":1806070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美中將簽第一階段貿易協定，專家：北京一大勝利","createTime":"2020-01-01T05:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T06:07:29.000Z","uid":173631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"946c36aefaacc72accfa833fe00e654764ec2721","tid":1806070,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2020/01/01/trump-will-sign-first-phase-of-us-china-trade-deal/[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2020%2F01%2F01%2Ftrump-will-sign-first-phase-of-us-china-trade-deal%2F%5B%2Furl&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=11712e75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2020/01/01/trump-will-sign-first-phase-of-us-china-trade-deal/[/url</a><br />\n美國總統川普今天表示，美中第一階段貿易協定將於 1 月 15 日簽署，並透露他將前往中國，繼續與北京磋商。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若干專家認為，這對北京而言可謂一大勝利。</span></span><img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/24/Tvb_hail_commie_winner.png/revision/latest?cb=20181215123622\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F24%2FTvb_hail_commie_winner.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20181215123622&h=9521c68c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川普在美股 2019 年最後一個交易日開盤前推文，為數週來充滿不確定性的美中第一階段貿易協定敲定簽署日期，但相關細節尚不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n華府和北京本月稍早宣布達成「第一階段」貿易協定，川普同意調降或取消部分關稅，北京則承諾進行貿易改革和擴大美國農產品進口，使雙方長達近兩年的貿易戰得以降溫。<br />\n<br />\n川普推文說：「我將於 1 月 15 日與中國簽署非常龐大且全面的第一階段貿易協定。儀式將在白宮舉行，中國高層代表將出席。」<br />\n<br />\n美中官員表示，協定內容包括保護智慧財產、糧食和農產品、金融服務和外匯及解決爭端的機制。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特海澤（Robert Lighthizer）說，根據這項新協定，中國同意在未來兩年內增加至少2000億美元的美國商品、農產品、能源產品和服務採購。<br />\n<br />\n川普今天除了宣布與中國簽署第一階段貿易協定的時程，還說他「稍後」將前往北京，展開第二階段對話，投資人深受鼓舞，美股今天收高。<br />\n<br />\n儘管如此，若干經濟學家和貿易專家認為，第一階段貿易協定對北京而言，可謂一大勝利。<br />\n<br />\n美國製造業聯盟（Alliance for American Manufacturing）主席保羅（Scott Paul）說，同意撤銷關稅意味「我們放棄很多籌碼，同時迴避了美中之間最有意義的貿易問題」。美國製造業聯盟支持川普對中國採取強硬的貿易立場。<br />\n<br />\n在中國經濟成長放緩和香港政治動盪之際，美中簽署第一階段貿易協定也讓中國國家主席習近平鬆了口氣。<br />\n<br />\n ]"},{"pid":"16a26f352bfd778bb82df776e7dd5b658e4dc2b6","tid":1806070,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"日日都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c01be161fa6009f37ed87087d860ce61533951","tid":1806070,"uid":288707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fcwmFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfcwmFJ.jpg&h=89b73ac5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfbdf1e5b6f7977f832934817b4051ae36185360","tid":1806070,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"中國又赢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f6721bf8e96e68d06377a0cdcc54524b9a09b5","tid":1806070,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"4c76429b568c093e92579ebd708719b1408cc1b5","tid":1806070,"uid":54959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"俾人打到仆街打咗年幾，依家人哋打少幾拳，當贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc556a4ed179c841bf2c33619b374dfaf525709","tid":1806070,"uid":48458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c76429b568c093e92579ebd708719b1408cc1b5","tid":1806070,"uid":54959,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"俾人打到仆街打咗年幾，依家人哋打少幾拳，當贏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T0