730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"美國每日打中國10拳，而家特朗普話，好啦，你每日比10蚊我，我每日打少你5拳。<br />\n<br />\n中國：yeah!我贏咗啦"},{"pid":"7db72726ee63c852507322e592f95b2e0768cb3d","tid":1806070,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"想知當年清政府簽完約後啲報紙係點吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d259d9cdac334d48e1d45ec40d41621dd31940","tid":1806070,"uid":280752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"簽又贏唔簽又贏。"}]}